<p>
which is a <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/NormalDistribution.html=
">normal distribution</a>. The binomial distribution is therefore approxima=
ted by a <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/NormalDistribution.html">=
normal
