lDistribution/Inline177.svg" class=3D"inlineformula" style=3D"max-height:10=
0%;max-width:100%" border=3D"0" width=3D"9" height=3D"21" alt=3D"lambda">.
</p>
<p>
Let <img src=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/images/equations/BinomialDist=
ribution/Inline178.svg" class=3D"inlineformula" style=3D"max-height:100%;ma=
x-width:100%" border=3D"0" width=3D"9" height=3D"21" alt=3D"x">
