=3D(P(x=3Di)P(y=3Dk-i))/(P(x+y=3Dk))=20
=3D((n; i)p^i(1-p)^(n-i)(m; k-i)p^(k-i)(1-p)^(m-(k-i)))/((n+m; k)p^k(1-p)^(=
n+m-k))=20
=3D((n; i)(m; k-i))/((n+m; k)).  "></td><td align=3D"right" width=3D"3">
